---
title: "Glucose Processing: Type Resolution Chain"
---
flowchart TD
    Arrive([Payload received]) --> PayloadField{glucoseProcessing\nin payload?}

    PayloadField -->|"Yes, valid"| UsePayload[Use payload value]
    PayloadField -->|"Yes, invalid"| Reject([400 Bad Request])
    PayloadField -->|No| SourceConfig{"device/app matches\na source default rule?\n(starts-with, ordered)"}

    SourceConfig -->|Yes| UseSource[Use source default]
    SourceConfig -->|No| IsConnector{Server-side\nconnector?}

    IsConnector -->|Yes| UseConnector["Use connector config\n(default: Smoothed)"]
    IsConnector -->|No| NoneResolved["GlucoseProcessing = null"]

    UsePayload --> Resolved([Processing type resolved])
    UseSource --> Resolved
    UseConnector --> Resolved
    NoneResolved --> Resolved
